---
import {
  SectionHeader
} from "../../components";
---

<section class="summary-section">

  <SectionHeader
    eyebrow="Portfolio First"
    title="This is more than 'just a CV'"
    intro="This portfolio is designed to show not only what I've done, but how my experience connects across projects, disciplines and technologies."
  />

  <div class="summary-content">

    <p>
      I specialise in delivering technical change across IP communications,
      digital transformation and data-driven decision making. My experience
      spans project delivery, product ownership and technical subject matter
      expertise across IP communications, CRM, software development, data
      analytics and cybersecurity.
    </p>

    <p>
      I take pride in never backing down from a new challenge and in building
      a solid technical understanding of every product, platform or project I
      work on. I'm very much a <em>"Never Stop Never Stopping"</em> kind of
      person; always curious, always learning and always looking for the next
      opportunity to improve.
    </p>

    <p>
      Rather than presenting isolated skills or job titles, this portfolio
      explores how those experiences connect through real projects,
      technologies, outcomes and the lessons learned along the way.
    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<style>

.summary-section{
    padding:3rem 0;
    border-top:1px solid #334155;
}

.summary-content{
    max-width:820px;
}

.summary-content p{
    color:#cbd5e1;
    line-height:1.8;
    font-size:1.05rem;
}

.summary-content p + p{
    margin-top:1.5rem;
}

</style>